{"tid":1545083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益，面對藍絲/狗嘅嗌交技巧","createTime":"2019-09-05T19:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T20:08:02.000Z","uid":279957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7bd83ceff34c54186c462810d1feb6b7e64aa1fc","tid":1545083,"uid":279957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:23:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母你四個字已經被廣泛使用，其實聽到有啲悶，有部份人甚至對呢四個字已經冇乜反應，不如大家集思廣益，係講粗口之餘，都可以有多啲K.O.敵人嘅技巧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1-遇着廢老撕紙狗：撕一貼百，撕到你落棺材嗰日你都未撕完，我係廢青不過你係就死嘅廢老！我長命過你，黐埋你副棺材都得!<br />\n<br />\n2-晚晚對住警察嗌黑警不如改嗌：&rdquo;721唔見人，831打死人&rdquo; 你不停嗌毅進仔，其實大把老屎忽當耳邊風，根本都唔關佢事"},{"pid":"967a38baaa71be71d51a2f9d34d858af9c40edac","tid":1545083,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:24:19.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f36f38434e4e5b882a33bf0ce13225bce6ea93d9","tid":1545083,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:08:02.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 出咗不反對啦！【9月6 反濫捕 抗威權 遮打集會】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543083</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]9.6遮打反濫暴抗威權集會 已獲批不反對通知書<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agyFBwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agyFBwU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTsuWvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTsuWvi.jpg&h=59781468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-